{"questionId":"14474714","questionHtml":"<p>In the case where&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>d</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>10</mn></math>. find the value of&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>q</mi><mo>-</mo><mi>p</mi></math>. Express your answer in the form of&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>a</mi><msqrt><mi>b</mi></msqrt></math>, where,&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>a</mi><mo>,</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mi>b</mi><mo>∈</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">ℤ</mi><mo>+</mo></msup></math>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mn>20</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>90</mn><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mfenced><mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mfenced></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>attempting to solve their 3 term quadratic equation&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>&nbsp;(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced><mrow><msup><mfenced><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>10</mn></mrow></mfenced><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mfenced></math>&nbsp;</strong></em>or&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced><mrow><mfenced><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo></mrow></mfenced><mfrac><mrow><mn>20</mn><mo>±</mo><msqrt><msup><mfenced><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>20</mn></mrow></mfenced><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>90</mn></msqrt></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></mfenced></math></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>-</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><msqrt><mn>10</mn></msqrt></math><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced><mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>p</mi></mrow></mfenced></math>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"h